Classify the student's message. Return ONLY valid JSON, no other text.

{
  "intent": one of ["learn", "practice", "exam_prep", "progress", "greeting", "off_topic"],
  "subject": subject name or null,
  "grade": integer or null,
  "topic": topic description or null
}

Intent definitions:
- "learn": student wants an explanation, help understanding a concept, or asks "how do I" / "what is"
- "practice": student wants a question, exercise, or says "test me" / "give me a problem"
- "exam_prep": student asks about exam tips, mark allocation, paper 1 vs paper 2, or past papers
- "progress": student asks what to study next, what they've covered, or where they are
- "greeting": hi, hello, thanks, bye
- "off_topic": anything not related to studying

Available curriculum:
{% for grade, subjects in available_curriculum.items() %}
- Grade {{ grade }}: {{ subjects | join(", ") }}
{% endfor %}

Only use grade and subject combinations from this list. If the student mentions a subject or grade not available, set it to null.

{% if session_grade %}
Current session: Grade {{ session_grade }}, {{ session_subject }}
{% endif %}
{% if current_topic %}
Currently studying: {{ current_topic }}
{% endif %}

Examples:
- "Help me understand quadratic equations" → {"intent": "learn", "subject": "Mathematics", "grade": null, "topic": "quadratic equations"}
- "Ngicela ungichazele nge-arithmetic sequence" → {"intent": "learn", "subject": "Mathematics", "grade": null, "topic": "arithmetic sequences"}
- "Give me a question on sequences" → {"intent": "practice", "subject": "Mathematics", "grade": null, "topic": "sequences"}
- "Test me on calculus" → {"intent": "practice", "subject": "Mathematics", "grade": null, "topic": "calculus"}
- "What tips for paper 1?" → {"intent": "exam_prep", "subject": "Mathematics", "grade": null, "topic": null}
- "How many marks is sequences worth?" → {"intent": "exam_prep", "subject": "Mathematics", "grade": null, "topic": "sequences"}
- "What should I study next?" → {"intent": "progress", "subject": null, "grade": null, "topic": null}
- "Hi" → {"intent": "greeting", "subject": null, "grade": null, "topic": null}
- "Who won the PSL?" → {"intent": "off_topic", "subject": null, "grade": null, "topic": null}